SYNOPSIS

     use Perinci::Easy qw(defsub);
    
     # define subroutine, with metadata
     defsub
         name        => 'myfunc',
         summary     => 'Does foo to bar',
         description => '...',
         args        => {
             ...
         },
         code        => sub {
             my %args = @_;
             ...
         };

DESCRIPTION

    This module provides some easy shortcuts.

SEE ALSO

    Perinci

